caption:
Stop by this weekend for a Kouign Amann! A flaky buttery croissant-like pastry that is caramelized on the outside. Available Saturday and Sunday weekly at our @rdgterminalmkt location. 

Shop @metropolitanbakery bread and pastries at both our Reading Terminal Market store (open daily) and Elkins Park store (closed Sunday). We look forward to seeing you!
